Interface CommonTypeDeclaration

All Superinterfaces:
JSOM
All Known Subinterfaces:
AnnotationDeclaration, ClassDeclaration, EnumDeclaration, InterfaceDeclaration, LocalClassDeclaration
public interface CommonTypeDeclaration
extends JSOM

This JSOM type is the base type for all kinds of type declarations, i.e. for classes, interfaces and so on.
